	Write a program using the following steps.
1- Declare a constant n (in this case we use n =5).
2- Declare an array T made of n integers.
3- Ask the user for the elements of the array T.
4- Write a function to find the largest value in the array.
5- Write a function to calculate the sum of all the values in the array.
6- Write a function to print for the user the numbers of the array from the smallest to the largest.
7- Call all the functions above and print the results.
